            <title class="- topic/title " xtrc="title:3;107:20" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/binding-controlled-values-to-attribute.dita">Example: Binding an attribute to an empty set</title>
            <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:7;108:16" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/binding-controlled-values-to-attribute.dita">The following code fragment declares that there are no valid values for the
                    <xmlatt class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlatt " xtrc="xmlatt:6;109:29" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/binding-controlled-values-to-attribute.dita">outputclass</xmlatt> attribute.</p>
            <codeblock class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xml:space="preserve" xtrc="codeblock:2;110:24" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/binding-controlled-values-to-attribute.dita">&lt;subjectScheme&gt;
  &lt;enumerationdef&gt;
    &lt;attributedef name="outputclass"/&gt;
    &lt;subjectdef/&gt;
  &lt;/enumerationdef&gt;
&lt;/subjectScheme&gt;</codeblock>
